{"id":232711836,"title":"#高雄講座 1/4 (六) 世界觸手可及-「愛吠的狗」零距離的沉浸式娛樂體驗","content":"http://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEG.jpg\n 【DAKUO創業之星講座】 \n \n「愛吠的狗娛樂」專長於AR/VR互動遊戲開發。高雄捷運公司合作於中央公園捷運站點設立了“XR未來日”展館，是國內少數具有研發能力並同時經營線下VR體驗店的業者之一。2019年推出首款恐怖VR遊戲--\"殭屍山莊\"，榮獲經濟部數位內容最佳產品獎項提名、國際知名VRCore「組委會選擇獎」、中國獨立遊戲製作大賽 IndiePlay「最佳VR遊戲」獎項提名！\n「愛吠的狗」開發多款VR遊戲，並接軌市場、發展線下體驗店，實際獲得遊戲玩家的第一手回饋。\n\n【講座大鋼】\n1. 創業與創作心得分享，研發團隊如何更貼近市場消費者\n2.XR(延展實境)產業的市場趨勢與發展策略\n備註：XR(延展實境)為AR(擴增實境), VR(虛擬實境)等應用之總稱。\n\n ❣報名連結👉 \n https://dakuo.pse.is/KJ3ZX \n\n時間：1/4(六) 14:30-17:00\n地點：高雄市數位內容創意中心 (高雄市鹽埕區新樂街214號3F)","excerpt":"【DAKUO創業之星講座】「愛吠的狗娛樂」專長於AR/VR互動遊戲開發。高雄捷運公司合作於中央公園捷運站點設立了“XR未來日”展館，是國內少數具有研發能力並同時經營線下VR體驗店的業者之一。2019年","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2bb20844-07ec-41d3-830f-ae551fc31246","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-18T11:25:28.981Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T11:25:28.981Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["講座","高雄","VR","遊戲","創業"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"課程","forumAlias":"course","school":"國立臺北大學","department":"經濟學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEG.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6b91249f-e86b-40b2-8406-a65f585ce7d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEGl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEGl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEGl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-18T11:25:28.981Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T11:25:28.981Z"},{"id":"6b91249f-e86b-40b2-8406-a65f585ce7d0","url":"http://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEG.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/CRkyKEG","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/CRkyKEGl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNO